":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲港女成日都睇唔起連登仔 連登仔就捉住港女黎屌 比啲威勢隻臭貨睇下 隻港女口裏說不 但身體很誠實 連登仔屌完 隻港女就想打佢一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啦好咁嘔心啦...邊個會想比連登班垃圾仔屌呀 ff少陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3294c70645a65fe06b49d0ecdc5239e1b792d6e2","tid":481973,"uid":120801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲港女成日都睇唔起連登仔 連登仔就捉住港女黎屌 比啲威勢隻臭貨睇下 隻港女口裏說不 但身體很誠實 連登仔屌完 隻港女就想打佢一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFf得咁具體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁160都ff成高佬la"},{"pid":"9eca515d5b84e6544776a8e431ce4412a531aa54","tid":481973,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻貓雙眼好撚迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連隻狗都有女食</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係貓公呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n🌻🍩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba83fbd99d68690048fe9c7ea8404f151d801824","tid":481973,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓仔un完貓女之後，貓女好痛會大叫+打條仔<br />\n因為佢條嘢有倒刺，「蚊」出黎果下既痛先可以刺激排卵。<br />\n<br />\n我頭先google左狗陰莖 原來一樣有倒刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能真係插搞左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後生一隻好可愛Ge貓狗 定狗貓"},{"pid":"f66b5543d3147b14cb60ae0d71296ca6ca8c6359","tid":481973,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s